### Google OAuth API Test Cases
### POST /api/auth/google
### 
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@contentType = application/json

### ✅ Test 1: New User Registration via Google
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/google
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "googleId": "123456789012345678901",
  "email": "google.user.test@example.com",
  "name": "Google User",
  "profilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/default-user"
}

### ✅ Test 2: Existing User Login via Google
### Note: Run Test 1 first, then run this test with the same googleId
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/google
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "googleId": "123456789012345678901",
  "email": "google.user.test@example.com",
  "name": "Google User",
  "profilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/default-user"
}

